            "title": "美股惊现集体跳水！加密市场逆势狂飙，比特币冲击 10 万美元大关",
            "id": 985447,
            "description": "<div class=\"centerarticle\">\n <p class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"><b><strong class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__textBold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">TradingKey - 加密市场独立于<a class=\"_internal_link_\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fx168news.com/info/001003/001003001\">美股</a>上涨，<a class=\"_internal_link_\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fx168news.com/quote/BINBTC\">比特币</a>继续反弹走强，有望突破10万美元关口。</strong></b></p>\n <p class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">周四（1月15日），</span><a href=\"https://www.tradingkey.com/analysis/cryptocurrencies/more/251255961-cryptocurrency-crypto-bitcoin-btc-eth-xrp-bnb-usdt-tradingkey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__link\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"></span></a><a class=\"_internal_link_\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fx168news.com/info/001008\">加密货币</a><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">延续涨势，总市值过去24小时上涨0.26%，升至3.26万亿美元。比特币 (</span><a href=\"https://www.tradingkey.com/analysis/cryptocurrencies/btc/250435634-crypto-btc-bitcoin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__link\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">BTC</span></a><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">) 今日涨超1%，</span><b><strong class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__textBold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">一度逼近9.8万美元，创下去年11月以来新高。</strong></b></p>\n <div class=\"braft-img-container\" data-src=\"https://static.fx168api.com/img/user/2f696af18fd126e5efbae66c3b9d132c/20260115150720158.png\">\n  <img src=\"https://static.fx168api.com/img/user/2f696af18fd126e5efbae66c3b9d132c/20260115150720158.png\" alt=\"bitcoin-btc-price-41b45dd6085b4157b4e70df5a68c1102\" width=\"800\" height=\"374\">\n </div><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">【比特币价格图表，来源：CoinMarketCap】</span>\n <p class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">不过，</span><b><strong class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__textBold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">表现最好的还是隐私板块。</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">过去24小时，隐私板块大涨1.54%，市值升至746亿美元。其中，达世币（DASH）暴涨超40%，Horizen（ZEN）大涨15%，门罗币（<a class=\"_internal_link_\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://brokers.fx168news.com/dealer/66e4c624287a17fb4ddfb8c35bd2184d\">XM</a>R）涨超7%，大零币 (</span><a href=\"https://www.tradingkey.com/analysis/cryptocurrencies/more/251206825-cryptocurrency-privacy-zcash-zec-price-tradingkey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__link\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">ZEC</span></a><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">) 上涨3%。</span></p>\n <p class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">与之不同，美国<a class=\"_internal_link_\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fx168news.com/info/001003\">股市</a>迎来下跌行情。其中，</span><b><strong class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__textBold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">美股三大指数齐跌，</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">纳指大跌1.00%，<a class=\"_internal_link_\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fx168news.com/quote/SPCIW\">标普500</a>下跌0.53%，<a class=\"_internal_link_\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fx168news.com/quote/INDIW\">道指</a>跌0.08%。</span><b><strong class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__textBold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">大型科技股集体跳水</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">，博通 (</span><a href=\"https://www.tradingkey.com/markets/stocks/nasdaq-avgo\" class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__link\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">AVGO</span></a><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">) 大跌超4%，而微软 (</span><a href=\"https://www.tradingkey.com/markets/stocks/nasdaq-msft\" class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__link\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">MSFT</span></a><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">)、亚马逊 (</span><a href=\"https://www.tradingkey.com/markets/stocks/nasdaq-amzn\" class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__link\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">AMZN</span></a><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">) 与Meta (</span><a href=\"https://www.tradingkey.com/markets/stocks/nasdaq-meta\" class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__link\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">META</span></a><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">) 均跌超2%，英伟达 (</span><a href=\"https://www.tradingkey.com/markets/stocks/nasdaq-nvda\" class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__link\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">NVDA</span></a><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">) 与特斯拉 (</span><a href=\"https://www.tradingkey.com/markets/stocks/nasdaq-tsla\" class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__link\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">TSLA</span></a><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">)也跌超1%。</span></p>\n <p class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n <div class=\"braft-img-container\" data-src=\"https://static.fx168api.com/img/user/2f696af18fd126e5efbae66c3b9d132c/20260115150720784.png\">\n  <img src=\"https://static.fx168api.com/img/user/2f696af18fd126e5efbae66c3b9d132c/20260115150720784.png\" alt=\"nvda-tsla-tsm-apple-goog-amzn-msft-f4c0efba12844249a1c0ab95676391b9\" width=\"800\" height=\"792\">\n </div><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">【大型科技股的涨跌幅，来源：Tradingkey】</span>\n <p class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"><b><strong class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__textBold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">美股本次跳水的导火索是美国对芯片下重手。</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">当地时间1月14日，美国总统特朗普宣布对这类芯片征收25%的关税，即在美国“过境”但随后被用于数据中心服务器等产品并最终出口至其他国家的芯片。特朗普还宣称，预计可以从中获得数十亿美元收入。</span></p>\n <p class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">2025年10月之后，<a class=\"_internal_link_\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fx168news.com/quote/BINBTC\">比特币</a>与<a class=\"_internal_link_\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fx168news.com/info/001003/001003001\">美股</a>相关性逐渐下降，走势出现明显的分化。其中，纳指维持高位盘整，道指与标普500相继攀升创新高，而比特币价格持续回调。11月21日之后，比特币价格触底反弹，总体趋势与美股三大指数再次保持一致。</span></p>\n <p class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n <div class=\"braft-img-container\" data-src=\"https://static.fx168api.com/img/user/2f696af18fd126e5efbae66c3b9d132c/20260115150721571.png\">\n  <img src=\"https://static.fx168api.com/img/user/2f696af18fd126e5efbae66c3b9d132c/20260115150721571.png\" alt=\"bitcoin-usa-stock-ac8a6129f06c4944aa78027cee42b0c0\" width=\"800\" height=\"375\">\n </div><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">【<a class=\"_internal_link_\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fx168news.com/quote/BINBTC\">比特币</a>、美股三大指数走势图，来源：TradingView】</span>\n <p class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">目前，</span><b><strong class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__textBold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><a class=\"_internal_link_\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fx168news.com/info/001003/001003001\">美股</a>转弱但比特币继续反弹走高，极有可能继续吸引资金回流加密市场。</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">过去三天，比特币现货ETF资金持续流入。1月13日，<a class=\"_internal_link_\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fx168news.com/quote/BINBTC\">比特币</a>现货ETF净流入约7.6亿美元，</span><b><strong class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__textBold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">创去年10月暴跌以来最大单日资金流入。</strong></b></p>\n <p class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n <div class=\"braft-img-container\" data-src=\"https://static.fx168api.com/img/user/2f696af18fd126e5efbae66c3b9d132c/20260115150722352.png\">\n  <img src=\"https://static.fx168api.com/img/user/2f696af18fd126e5efbae66c3b9d132c/20260115150722352.png\" alt=\"bitcoin-btc-etf-97583b69cfd44b159538ab3d5d1ae147\" width=\"800\" height=\"351\">\n </div><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">【比特币现货ETF资金流动图，来源：Coinglass】</span>\n <p class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">在摩根大通看来，<a class=\"_internal_link_\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fx168news.com/info/001008/\">加密资产</a>资金在2025年将流入1300亿美元，而</span><b><strong class=\"PlaygroundEditorTheme__textBold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">2026年继续流入而且可能增加。</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">摩根大通分析师指出，美国《明晰法案》（Clarity Act）等加密监管落实将促使机构采用数字资产。若如此，比特币不仅会突破10万美元，甚至可能突破历史高点。</span></p>\n <p><a href=\"https://www.tradingkey.com/zh-hans/analysis/cryptocurrencies/btc/261477590-crypto-bitcoin-btc-etf-price-stock-usa-clarity-act-tradingkey\" target=\"_self\">原文链接</a></p>\n</div>\n<script src=\"https://static.fx168api.com/js/jquery-1.12.3.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://static.fx168api.com/js/fx168_ny_addad.js?t=202409051358\"></script>\n<div style=\"\n    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;\n    margin: 0.3rem 0.2rem 0;\n    padding-bottom: 0.2rem;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    color: #333;\n    font-size:16px;\n    line-height:2;\n\">\n <div>\n  敬告读者：本文为转载发布，不代表本网站赞同其观点和对其真实性负责。FX168财经仅提供信息发布平台，文章或有细微删改。\n </div>\n</div>",
